metadata.name: IN PLAIN SIGHT
metadata.description:
The underwater world is filled with amazing sights and colors. If you ever find yourself beneath that thin blue layer that separates our worlds, make sure to take it slow and look around.

Some things can be hidden in plain sight!!

//
